{
  "texts": [
    "Such a question leads to another key measure for AI risk assessment-AI harm.",
    "HarmAI harm can occur to individuals, organizations, and societies.",
    "For example, AI may cause physical harm to individual patients, damage a hospital's reputation owing to AI incidents, and even endanger society if it is weaponized (eg, being used to disrupt the global drug manufacturing and supply chain).",
    "Hence, AI harm is a risk measure highly related to AI responsibility and trustworthiness.",
    "Developing trustworthy AI and following responsible AI practices can reduce or avoid AI harm.It is worth mentioning that some of the metrics we proposed here pass some human characteristics into AI."
  ]
}